  <brief_title>Education Intervention to Reduce Helminth Infections and Absenteeism in Grade 5 School-children</brief_title>
  <official_title>Effectiveness of a Post-deworming Education Intervention to Reduce Soil-transmitted Helminth Infections and Absenteeism in Grade 5 School-children in a Community of Extreme Poverty, Peruvian Amazon</official_title>
  <sponsors>
